        explanation: 'OData $batch groups multiple read/write operations into a single HTTP multipart request. The server processes each operation and returns all responses bundled together. In SAPUI5, ODataModel V4 has auto-batching enabled by default. In V2, batch mode can be enabled with model.setUseBatch(true). This drastically reduces the number of HTTP round trips from 40 to 1.',
