        explanation: 'The robust approach: (1) CDS DCLS (Data Control Language Statement) restricts which users can read the field at the OData level — HR Managers get the value, others get null/empty. (2) @UI.fieldControl references a calculated field using authority-check logic — returns 0 (hidden) for non-managers. This enforces security at both data access and UI levels.',
